  <text xml:lang="ta">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="Aink58-kilavi">
        <p type="edition">talaimakaṟkup puṟattoḻukkam uḷatāyiṟṟu eṉpatu kēṭṭa tōḻi avaṉai viṉāyatu.
        </p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"> </p>
      </div>
      <div xml:id="Aink58">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l>viṇṭu vaṉṉa veṇṇeṟ pōrviṟ</l>
          <l>kaivaṇ virāa ṉiruppai yaṉṉa</l>
          <l>vivaḷaṇaṅ kuṟṟaṉai pōṟi</l>
          <l>piṟarkku maṉaiyaiyāl vāḻi nīyē.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">



          <l> You seem rather tormented by this girl</l>
          <l> who is like Iruppai,</l>
          <l rend="indent2"> [that city] of Virāṉ, the liberal of hand, </l>
          <l rend="indent2"> with its mountainous heaps of white paddy – </l>
          <l> [And yet] you are to be found the houses of other women [too]. </l>
          <l> Long life to you! </l>


        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
